  "description": "\ud83c\udfae GPU pressure on the bare-metal Ollama host (.240, RTX 5090). Read top\u2192bottom: how busy is the card \u2192 how saturated is VRAM \u2192 how hot is it \u2192 how is request latency tracking GPU pressure. Empty until you set up nvidia-gpu-exporter or Alloy's nvidia integration on .240 \u2014 see the panel descriptions for the metric names expected.",
